README erlmail-0.0.1


%% =====================================================================
This is the initial release of ErlDir, as such it is incomplete and 
possibly unstable.


Please check the HISTORY and TODO files for more information on the 
current status of new features or known bugs.

%% =====================================================================

Currently ErlMail is dependant on util-0.0.1 which is also availabe for 
download form http://www.erlmail.com, Mostly for some date/time funcations
This dependancy will be removed in later versions.

%% =====================================================================

Please direct any comments or patches to sjackson@simpleenigma.com with
ErlMail in the subject line.